scions.insc_cntn: The best part of marrying you, Aries, is the adventure. You're always going to have fun ideas for date night, even after you've been married for years. You'll never run out of surprises for your partner, which will keep the relationship exciting.

Out of the chaos comes order. In the midst of the void, a pattern is discernable. Within this pattern, consciousness is born and the spring of human spiritual endeavor can flow around the Earth and out into the boundless universe beyond.
